Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Harvey Milk killing
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040bxq6
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 27 May 1979
Gay outrage at lenient sentence for killer of Harvey Milk. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.